# Krasny Yar, Kizhinginsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Krasny Yar () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kizhinginsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 54 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Krasny Yar is located 10&nbsp;km north of Kizhinga (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kizhinga is the nearest rural locality.
